Directed by Remo D’Souza

Written by Farhad Samji

Cast Varun Dhawan (Sahej). Shraddha Kapoor (Inayat). Prabhu Deva (Ram Prasad). Nora Fatehi (Mia). Aparshakti Khurana (Amrinder). Dharmesh Yelande (D). Salman Yusuff Khan (Zayn). Punit Pathak (Inder). Raghav Juyal (Poddy). Sushant Pujari (Sushi). Caroline Wilde (Alisha). Sonam Bajwa (Pammi). Vartika Jha (Samaira).Gopuu Ali. Nikita Anand (Rhea). Jesus Soria Antalen (Bboy). Aayan Aziz (Anna Tarakanova). Dev Barot (Dancer). Pravin Bhosale (Pravin). Kristina Chudo (Aarav Shyam). Max Cook (Joe Baddley). Amerjit Deu (Iqbal Khan). Shashank Dogra (Aamir). Sami Finn (Vadim Lebedev). Adriano Ratto Gal (Alex). Divyesh Gandhi (Preetinder).Jazz Gee.Nisha George. Leo Graham (Amaira Gupta). Monisha Hassen (Inayat’s Mother). Sammy Jonas Heaney (Backing Dancer (as Sammy John Heaney)). Jai Hickling (Jai). Corinne Holt (Royals crew). Abdul Hakim Joy (Dancer). Rajesh Kalhan (Rajwinder). Dominykas Karcemarskas (Kayleigh Ashworth).Radhika Kashyap. Umair Khalil (Faris Inayat). Adnan Khan (Illegal Immigrant 3). Javed Khan (Inayat’s Father). Rehaan Khan (Illegal Immigrant 4). Vinay Khandelwal (Faiz). Sushant Khatri (Chotu). Priyanshu Khurana (Sardar 3). Dimple Kumar (Homeless Immigrant). Michael Lumb (Illegal Immigrant). Bharat Mistri (Homeless Immigrant).Shakti Mohan.Akanksha Singh Mourya. Manisha Nagar (Customer Manisha). Parvinder Nandhra (Immigrant Boss Raja). Manoj Pahwa (Chabbra). Seema Parmar (Sister in Law (credit only)). Hiten Patel (Police Officer).Sheetal Pery. Raj Phagania (Immigrant). Sneya Rajani (Dancer). Pavan Rao (Fahad). Francis T Roughley (Mark).Shyraa Roy. Mariana Salazar (Dancer). Miroslav Sekula (Mira). Dahab Shahzad (Daniel Anastasia). Hibba Shahzad (Dornatella). Atul Sharma (Homeless Immigrant). Avinashi Sharma (Homeless Immigrant). Murali Sharma (UK Cop (as Murli Sharma)). Nivedita Sharma (Nivi). Prashant Shinde (Sam). Pravin Shinde (Naussef). Chobber Sidhu (Dialogue Writter). Abhinay Raj Singh (Dancer in group). Bhupinder Singh (Omar). Deependra Singh (Rohit). Gunveet Singh (Gurinder). Praminder Singh (Illegal Immigrant 2). Vickrem Singh (Illegal Immigrant (as Vickrem Gill)). John Stableforth (Rick (credit only)). Jaydeep Tank (Homeless Immigrant).Poppin Ticko. Aklima Uddin (Dancer). Ramesh Vethanayagam (Illegal Immigrant 1). Zarina Wahab (Amrinder’s Mother). Rina Yadav (Airport Passenger). Minhaz Zee (Jag). Izabela Zieba (Dancer). Susana Campesino (Ballet teacher (uncredited)). Garbriella Cuffy ((uncredited)). Melissa Kibris (Dancer (uncredited)). Phoebe Lourdes (Street Dancer (uncredited)). Upasana Singh (Pammi’s Mother (uncredited)). Chandni Srivastava (Chandni (uncredited)). Victoria Rose Wilson (Dancer (uncredited))

Languages Hindi

Producers Vivek Bhatnagar. Shiv Chanana. Ravi Chaturvedi. Sanjana Chopra. Lizelle Dsouza. Pawan Jam. Hetvi Karia. Bhushan Kumar. Krishan Kumar. Gabbar Sangrur. Sandeep Sharma. Yogiraj Shetty. Sarmad Varraich

Production SVO Special Vehicle Operation. Remo D’Souza Entertainment. T-Series
